# Coltex Dataset — License Summary

Copyright 2026 Elijah Maxwell / Coltex

Coltex is offered under four license tiers. See [LICENSING.md](../LICENSING.md) for the full tier comparison and terms.

## Personal License ($79)

For students, hobbyists, and researchers. Non-commercial use only.

## Professional License ($399)

For freelancers, startups, and commercial developers. Includes Personal rights plus commercial use for one company or legal entity.

## Enterprise License (custom quote)

For medium and large businesses, government, education, and enterprises. Includes Professional rights plus organization-wide deployment, multiple teams, private/on-prem cloud, and enterprise services per agreement.

## Dataset EULA

Supplemental terms for enterprise RAG vector dataset packages (chunks, embeddings, graph edges, benchmarks).

## Excluded paths

Files under `knowledge-base/_excluded_from_distribution/` and
`knowledge-base/generated/` are not part of any product package.
